                                            <h6 class="mb-0 fw-bold"><i class="fa fa-money"></i> @obj.TotalVentasEfectivo <span class="d-block text-muted fw-normal"><i class="fa fa-credit-card"></i> @obj.TotalVentasTarjeta </span></h6>
                                        </td>
                                        <td>
                                            <h6 class="mb-0 fw-bold">E: @obj.TotalSalidas <span class="d-block text-muted fw-normal">S: @obj.TotalEntradas</span></h6>
                                        </td>
